### AI Quiz Platform - API Tests
### Use with VS Code "REST Client" extension
### Install: Extensions → search "REST Client" by Huachao Mao
### Click "Send Request" above each request to test

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### =============================================
### STEP 1: REGISTER A NEW USER
### =============================================

# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "first_name": "Test",
    "last_name": "User",
    "password": "MyPassword123!",
    "password_confirm": "MyPassword123!"
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 2: LOGIN
### =============================================

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "MyPassword123!"
}

###

# Copy the access token from the login response above
# Paste it below replacing YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### =============================================
### STEP 3: GET PROFILE
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 4: REFRESH ACCESS TOKEN
### =============================================

# @name refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/token/refresh/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "refresh": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 5: LIST YOUR DOCUMENTS
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 6: LIST YOUR QUIZZES
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 7: GENERATE A QUIZ
### (Replace document_id with your document's UUID)
### =============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/generate/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "document_id": "YOUR_DOCUMENT_UUID_HERE",
    "topic": "main concepts",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "num_questions": 5,
    "title": "My First Quiz",
    "time_limit_minutes": 10
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 8: GET QUIZ (without answers)
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/YOUR_QUIZ_UUID_HERE/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 9: GET QUIZ WITH ANSWERS (creator only)
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/YOUR_QUIZ_UUID_HERE/?with_answers=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 10: SUBMIT QUIZ ANSWERS
### =============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/YOUR_QUIZ_UUID_HERE/submit/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "answers": [
        {"question_id": "QUESTION_1_UUID", "selected_option": "A"},
        {"question_id": "QUESTION_2_UUID", "selected_option": "B"},
        {"question_id": "QUESTION_3_UUID", "selected_option": "C"},
        {"question_id": "QUESTION_4_UUID", "selected_option": "D"},
        {"question_id": "QUESTION_5_UUID", "selected_option": "A"}
    ],
    "time_taken_seconds": 180
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 11: VIEW ATTEMPT HISTORY
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/attempts/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 12: VIEW ANALYTICS DASHBOARD
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 13: VIEW LEADERBOARD
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/leaderboard/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 14: VIEW ACCURACY OVER TIME (last 30 days)
### =============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/accuracy/?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 15: SEMANTIC SEARCH TEST
### =============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/rag/search/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "document_id": "YOUR_DOCUMENT_UUID_HERE",
    "query": "what is the main concept",
    "top_k": 3
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 16: LOGOUT
### =============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "refresh_token": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###

### =============================================
### STEP 17: CHANGE PASSWORD
### =============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "old_password": "MyPassword123!",
    "new_password": "NewPassword456!",
    "new_password_confirm": "NewPassword456!"
}

###

### =============================================
### FILTERING AND PAGINATION EXAMPLES
### =============================================

### List quizzes - page 2, 5 per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/?page=2&page_size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List quizzes - only hard difficulty
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/?difficulty=hard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search quizzes by title/topic
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/?search=python
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List documents - only processed ones
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/?status=processed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Attempt history - sorted by accuracy
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/attempts/?ordering=-accuracy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
